description.narrative:
General question: Results related to the intended outcome 2016Question: Summarise results related to the intended outcome (this information will be sent to Open Aid)Answer: The project has achieved it overall objective to support the Tax Administration in Moldova to initiate the implementation of a modern, fair and consistent system of tax administration; to promote voluntary tax compliance, to change its mandate to become a service provider and to enhance tax audit trough new methods and tools. The contribution was initially agreed for 2013-2016 however, a non-cost extension was decided for September 2016 - July 2017 due to the opportunity to support STS for the upcoming institutional reform. The overall most important achievements in this project are the following:  
- tax revenue has increased during the cooperation period compared to the period just before – even when some other factors as e.g. inflation has been accounted for; 
- the awareness of the importance of behavior and attitudes has increased in MSTI/STS and is now in focus in all interactions with taxpayers;
- voluntary compliance and confidence in the Tax Administration has increased in the society.
